# Pem backend (`backend/`)

**Package:** NestJS app under **`backend/`** — `npm install`, `npm run start:dev`, `npm run build` from `backend/`. No shared runtime code with `app/`.

**Stack:** **NestJS** ~11, **Drizzle ORM** + **`pg`**, **Clerk** JWT (**`jose`** + JWKS), **Svix** for `POST /webhooks/clerk`, **`@nestjs/throttler`**, **`@nestjs/swagger`** (`/docs` when not prod), **`ValidationPipe`**. **Config** — **`src/config/configuration.ts`**. **OpenAI** via **Vercel AI SDK v6** (`generateText` + `Output`, never `generateObject`). **Background work** lives under **`src/background/`** — see layout table. **Expo** push — **`notifyInboxUpdated`**. **No Tavily / SerpAPI / prep agents.**

**Tables (Drizzle: `src/database/schemas/`):** **`users`** (incl. **`timezone`** IANA), **`dumps`** (raw **`text`**, **`polished_text`**, **`status`**: `processing` \| `processed` \| `failed`), **`actionables`** (extracted items: tone, urgency, batch_key, dates, status), **`memory_facts`**.

**Drizzle:** Change schema in TS → **`npm run db:generate`** → review generated SQL → **`npm run db:migrate`**. Never hand-edit `drizzle/*.sql` or `drizzle/meta/`. Details: **`pem-project.mdc`** (*Drizzle workflow*).

**Layout:**

| Area | Role |
|------|------|
| `src/background/` | **Single Nest entry** for async work: **`BackgroundModule`** (`@Global`) registers BullMQ, dump worker, agents, inbox-events. Import **`BackgroundModule`** (not separate queue/extraction modules). |
| `src/background/agents/<name>/` | One folder per **LLM agent** (e.g. **`extraction/`** — `ExtractionService`, schema, module). Add new agents here. |
| `src/background/queues/dump/` | BullMQ **`dump`** queue: `DumpProcessor`, `DumpExtractService` (orchestrates extraction agent + DB + events). |
| `src/background/inbox-events/` | **Redis pub/sub** — workers `publish` per-dump events; **`InboxStreamService`** subscribes so **`GET /inbox/stream`** (SSE) pushes to the app. Bridges **worker process** ↔ **HTTP process**. Exported via **`BackgroundModule`**. |
| `src/dumps/` | `POST /dumps`, `GET /dumps`, `GET /dumps/:id` |
| `src/inbox/` | `GET /inbox`, `GET /inbox/all`, `GET /inbox/stream` (SSE) |
| `src/actionables/` | `GET /actionables/done`, `GET /actionables/:id`, PATCH done/dismiss/undone/undismiss/snooze |
| `src/users/` | `GET /users/me`, `PATCH /users/me/timezone`, profile, push token |
| `src/profile/` | `memory_facts` CRUD for `/users/me/profile` |
| `src/push/` | Expo push |
| `src/auth/`, `src/webhooks/`, `src/health/` | unchanged patterns |

**Security:** Validate input; use **`ClerkAuthGuard`** + DB user id from JWT.

**Maintenance:** When **schema, routes, queues, or env** change, update **this file** in the same effort as the code. See **`pem-project.mdc`** — *Keeping `.cursor/rules` in sync*.

**Collaboration:** See `pem-project.mdc`.
